At one point in time, Western nations used to lead the world in freedom. Now, not so much—especially when it comes to the left’s trans agenda. And in what is likely the most tyrannical news this week, an Australian women’s-rights activist has been ordered to pay $95,000 to two transgender athletes after referring to them in ways the court deemed discriminatory for their participation in women’s football.
